  <source>Hôpital Armand Trousseau</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to assess the Pupillary Pain Index before and after a bolus of alfentanil in
      children under general anesthesia, before skin incision.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
